    "Moreover, it is noteworthy that the comparison among various studies in the literature utilizes the histopathology dataset and employs the same loss formula, i.e., binary cross-entropy.",
    "This standardized approach enables researchers to make fair and meaningful comparisons.",
    "Consequently, this contributes to establishing a reliable benchmark for evaluating and advancing breast cancer classification models effectively.",
    "In section 4, we saw that the accuracy of the first suggested approach, a combination of CNN and EfficientNetV2B3, on the histopathology images was higher than that of the second, a combination of MobileNet and DenseNet121, and the third, a combination of MobileNetV2 and EfficientNetV2_b0.",
    "Thus, we established the first approach as our own, making it a more stable and effective deep learning strategy."
